{"tid":1661324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"五大訴求：原來沒有人想撤回國歌法","createTime":"2019-10-18T04:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T04:52:29.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1e3a5fedf37fa08873751faae16058c3afba81","tid":1661324,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"國歌法草案 本立法年度恢復二讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2476988/%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%20%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E4%BA%8C%E8%AE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2476988%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%2520%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%25AE%2580&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=3f7ed0d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2476988/%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%20%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E4%BA%8C%E8%AE%80</a><br />\n<br />\n港府盼早日通過實施國歌法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201910170242.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F201910170242.aspx&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=a25a4d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201910170242.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局向立法會提交文件指，立法會法案委員會在2018-19立法年度經過17次會議及逾50小時討論後，已於5月24日完成審議，並於6月14日向內務委員會作出報告，政府計劃在2019-20立法年度就《國歌條例草案》恢復二讀辯論，以期盡早通過。"},{"pid":"7db4f65e7f941ac9cced4b191f136d9856a2dc20","tid":1661324,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"儘管香港「反送中」運動觸發一股「反中」情緒，當局仍然希望立法會盡早通過國歌條例草案，以實施國歌法。<br />\n<br />\n本地媒體報導，政制及內地事務局近日向立法會提交文件指出，港府有責任在本地實施國歌法，立法會的國歌條例草案委員會此前已對草案進行了超過50小時的討論，政府計畫在新立法年度恢復二讀辯論，以期盡早通過草案。"},{"pid":"3a05dda8dad99408198f39d25a0fb1457063bda6","tid":1661324,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以撤回嗰部分包含所有針對香港人嘅惡化？ 包括國歌法、送中條例、公安條例同緊急法？<br />\n上面是但一樣都係搞鳩我哋㗎咋"},{"pid":"230912de97103b6de608a8b5c389a9acad1f7592","tid":1661324,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"國歌法：辱罵《中華人民共和國國歌》要坐三年監。"},{"pid":"06bc62f1af852c39cd96622abfa058895fb31747","tid":1661324,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a05dda8dad99408198f39d25a0fb1457063bda6","tid":1661324,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以撤回嗰部分包含所有針對香港人嘅惡化？ 包括國歌法、送中條例、公安條例同緊急法？<br />\n上面是但一樣都係搞鳩我哋㗎咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"緊急法和公安條例立左法，要修改法律，難度較高。<br />\n國歌法仲未立法，要撤回比較易。"},{"pid":"393a89cd512605fc22c48b6e82b03047ba0ad8a9","tid":1661324,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06bc62f1af852c39cd96622abfa058895fb31747","tid":1661324,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a05dda8dad99408198f39d25a0fb1457063bda6","tid":1661324,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以撤回嗰部分包含所有針對香港人嘅惡化？ 包括國歌法、送中條例、公安條例同緊急法？<br />\n上面是但一樣都係搞鳩我哋㗎咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"緊急法和公安條例立左法，要修改法律，難度較高。<br />\n國歌法仲未立法，要撤回比較易。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"咁最終都係要嗰啲所謂法律徹底消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedd6da236a9cd8b6a3551a7ceb1d83e66209172","tid":1661324,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過1